    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 in Silver Lining Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in solid overall condition, showing the pride of ownership despite expected signs of light use. The exterior retains a deep shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the lower rear bumper from typical parking. Inside, the Parchment leather interior is clean and strictly non-smoking; while there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the upholstery is free of rips or stains. All cabin electronics\u2014including the heated seats, navigation, and premium audio system\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, this Lexus is excellent. It has 65,000 miles on the odometer with a consistent service history. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change and new brake pads installed just 3,000 miles ago. The tires have approximately 60% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly. This is a dependable, premium SUV that balances luxury with longevity. Clean title in hand.",
